Key Match Events: Emilio Nsue scored a hat-trick for Equatorial Guinea with goals in the 21st, 51st, and 61st minutes.
José Miranda scored for Equatorial Guinea in the 46th minute.
Esteban Orozco scored an own goal for Equatorial Guinea in the 37th minute.
Zé Turbo scored for Guinea-Bissau in the 90+3rd minute.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was held at Stade Olympique Alassane Ouattara with an attendance of 13,888.
